#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:109
msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "Instellingen Opslaan"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:204
msgid "Default Filters"
msgstr "Standaardfilters"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:208
msgid "Hidden Activities"
msgstr "Verborgen activiteiten"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:212
msgid "Custom Post Types"
msgstr "Aangepaste Bericht Types"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:216
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "FAQ"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:277
msgid "Default Activity Filters"
msgstr "Standaard activiteitenfilters"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:278
msgid ""
"Configure the default activity filter for different contexts. These settings "
"determine what type of activities are shown by default when users visit "
"activity streams."
msgstr ""
"Configureer het standaard activiteitenfilter voor verschillende contexten. "
"Deze instellingen bepalen welk type activiteiten standaard wordt getoond "
"wanneer gebruikers activiteitenstromen bezoeken."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:285
msgid "Site-wide Activity Default"
msgstr "Site-brede activiteit Standaard"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:291
#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:313
msgid "Everything"
msgstr "Alles"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:300
msgid ""
"Default filter applied to the main site-wide activity stream. Users can "
"still change this using the activity filter dropdown."
msgstr ""
"Standaard filter dat wordt toegepast op de hoofdstroom van activiteiten op "
"de hele site. Gebruikers kunnen dit nog steeds wijzigen met de "
"vervolgkeuzelijst Activiteitenfilter."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:307
msgid "Profile Activity Default"
msgstr "Profiel Activiteit Standaard"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:324
msgid ""
"Default filter applied to individual user profile activity streams. Some "
"activity types like \"New Member\" are excluded as they don't typically "
"appear on user profiles."
msgstr ""
"Standaard filter toegepast op individuele gebruikersprofiel "
"activiteitenstromen. Sommige activiteitstypes zoals \"Nieuw lid\" zijn "
"uitgesloten omdat ze normaal niet verschijnen op gebruikersprofielen."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:345
msgid "Posted a status update"
msgstr "Statusupdate geplaatst"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:346
msgid "Replied to a status update"
msgstr "Gereageerd op een statusupdate"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:351
msgid "Hidden Activity Types"
msgstr "Verborgen activiteitstypen"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:352
msgid ""
"Select activity types to completely hide from all activity streams. Hidden "
"activities will not appear in the activity feed or filter dropdown options."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer activiteitstypes die je volledig wilt verbergen voor alle "
"activiteitenstromen. Verborgen activiteiten worden niet weergegeven in de "
"activiteitenfeed of in de vervolgkeuzelijsten voor filters."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:354
msgid "Activity Types to Hide"
msgstr "Te verbergen activiteitstypen"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:358
msgid ""
"No activity types available. Make sure BuddyPress is properly installed and "
"activated."
msgstr ""
"Geen activiteitstypes beschikbaar. Controleer of BuddyPress goed is "
"geïnstalleerd en geactiveerd."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:366
msgid "Core Activities (Always Available)"
msgstr "Kernactiviteiten (altijd beschikbaar)"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:369
msgid ""
"These essential activity types cannot be hidden as they are required for "
"basic BuddyPress functionality."
msgstr ""
"Deze essentiële activiteitstypen kunnen niet worden verborgen omdat ze nodig "
"zijn voor de basisfunctionaliteit van BuddyPress."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:387
msgid "Other Activity Types"
msgstr "Andere activiteitstypen"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:390
msgid "Check the boxes below to HIDE these activity types from your site."
msgstr ""
"Vink de vakjes hieronder aan om deze activiteitstypen te VERBORGEN van je "
"site."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:441
#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:489
msgid "How it works:"
msgstr "Hoe het werkt:"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:465
msgid "Custom Post Type Activities"
msgstr "Aangepaste Post Type Activiteiten"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:467
msgid ""
"Enable automatic activity generation for custom post types when they are "
"published. Only public custom post types with admin interface are available "
"for selection."
msgstr ""
"Automatische activiteitgeneratie inschakelen voor aangepaste posttypes "
"wanneer ze worden gepubliceerd. Alleen openbare aangepaste posttypes met "
"beheerinterface zijn beschikbaar voor selectie."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:470
msgid "Enable Post Types"
msgstr "Berichttypes inschakelen"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:475
msgid "No eligible custom post types found."
msgstr "Geen in aanmerking komende aangepaste posttypes gevonden."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:477
msgid ""
"Custom post types must be public, have admin UI enabled, and support posts "
"to appear here. Built-in WordPress post types (posts, pages) are not shown "
"as they have their own activity systems."
msgstr ""
"Aangepaste posttypes moeten openbaar zijn, admin UI ingeschakeld hebben en "
"posts ondersteunen om hier weergegeven te worden. Ingebouwde WordPress "
"berichttypes (berichten, pagina's) worden niet getoond omdat ze hun eigen "
"activiteitssystemen hebben."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:490
msgid ""
"When a post of the selected custom post type is published, an activity entry "
"will be automatically created showing the author, post type, and post title "
"with a link. Existing posts will not generate activities - only new posts "
"published after enabling this feature."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer een bericht van het geselecteerde aangepaste berichttype wordt "
"gepubliceerd, wordt automatisch een activiteit aangemaakt met de auteur, het "
"berichttype en de berichttitel met een link. Bestaande berichten genereren "
"geen activiteiten - alleen nieuwe berichten die worden gepubliceerd na het "
"inschakelen van deze functie."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:525
#, php-format
msgid "%d post"
msgid_plural "%d posts"
msgstr[0] "%d bericht"
msgstr[1] "%d berichten"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:539
msgid "Custom Activity Label (optional):"
msgstr "Aangepast activiteitslabel (optioneel):"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:548
msgid ""
"Leave empty to use the default post type name. This text will appear in "
"activity entries like \"John published a new [label]: Post Title\""
msgstr ""
"Leeg laten om de standaard posttypenaam te gebruiken. Deze tekst zal "
"verschijnen in activiteitsitems zoals \"John publiceerde een nieuwe [label]: "
"Titel bericht\""

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:564
msgid "Global Settings"
msgstr "Algemene Instellingen"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:572
msgid "Hide custom post type activities from site-wide activity stream"
msgstr ""
"Verberg aangepaste posttype activiteiten uit de site-brede activiteitenstroom"

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:574
msgid ""
"When enabled, custom post type activities will only appear in the author's "
"profile activity stream, not in the main site-wide activity feed. This helps "
"reduce clutter in the main activity stream while still giving authors credit "
"on their profiles."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer deze optie is ingeschakeld, verschijnen aangepaste posttype-"
"activiteiten alleen in de activiteitenstroom van het profiel van de auteur "
"en niet in de hoofdfeed van de site. Dit helpt om rommel in de "
"hoofdactiviteitstroom te verminderen terwijl auteurs nog steeds erkenning "
"krijgen op hun profiel."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:654
msgid "Security check failed. Please try again."
msgstr "Beveiligingscontrole is mislukt. Probeer het opnieuw."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:664
msgid "You do not have sufficient permissions to access this page."
msgstr "Je hebt niet voldoende rechten om deze pagina te bekijken."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:693
#: includes/class-wbcom-integration.php:271
#: includes/shared-admin/class-wbcom-shared-loader.php:790
msgid "Settings saved successfully."
msgstr "Instellingen succesvol opgeslagen."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:700
msgid "No changes were made to the settings."
msgstr "Er zijn geen wijzigingen aangebracht in de instellingen."

#: includes/class-bp-activity-filter-admin.php:710
#, php-format
